          <p>80+ garages</p>
        </div>
        <div class="city-card">
          <div class="city-icon">🌊</div>
          <h3>Kochi</h3>
          <p>60+ garages</p>
        </div>
        <div class="city-card">
          <div class="city-icon">🏔️</div>
          <h3>Lucknow</h3>
          <p>70+ garages</p>
        </div>
        <div class="city-card">
          <div class="city-icon">🌾</div>
          <h3>Chandigarh</h3>
          <p>50+ garages</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ====== TESTIMONIALS ====== -->
  <section class="section section-alt" id="testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Car Owners Say</h2>
        <p>Don't take our word for it — hear from our happy customers</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>Booked a full service for my Honda City. They picked it up at 9 AM from my office and delivered by 4 PM — fully washed and sanitised. The live video updates were a game changer. Saved ₹3,000 vs the Honda dealership!</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar">RK</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Rajesh Kumar</h4>
              <span>Honda City, Mumbai</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>As a working mother, I never had time to take my car for service. DriveEase solved that completely. They picked up my Creta from home, and I could track the entire service on my phone. The courtesy car they provided was a lifesaver!</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar">PS</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Priya Sharma</h4>
              <span>Hyundai Creta, Bangalore</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>I was paying ₹8,000+ at the Maruti dealer for my Brezza service. Tried DriveEase on a friend's recommendation — got better service at ₹4,999 with genuine parts and a 1-year warranty. Switched permanently.</p>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="testimonial-avatar">AV</div>
            <div>
              <h4>Amit Verma</h4>
              <span>Maruti Brezza, Delhi NCR</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ====== LEAD FORM ====== -->
  <section class="lead-section" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="lead-info">
        <h2>Get Your Free Service Quote in 60 Seconds</h2>
        <p>Tell us about your car and we'll give you an instant, no-obligation quote with transparent pricing. No hidden costs, ever.</p>
        <ul class="lead-benefits">
          <li>Free doorstep pickup and delivery</li>
          <li>40% cheaper than authorised dealerships</li>
          <li>100% genuine OEM spare parts</li>
          <li>1-year warranty on all services</li>
          <li>Live video updates during service</li>
          <li>Free car wash and interior vacuuming</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="lead-form-card">
        <h3>Get Your Free Quote</h3>
        <p class="subtitle">We'll call you within 15 minutes</p>
        <form id="quickLeadForm">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="name">Full Name *</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="phone">Phone Number *</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="Enter 10-digit mobile number" required pattern="[0-9]{10}" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="city">City *</label>
              <select id="city" name="city" required>
                <option value="">Select City</option>
                <option>Mumbai</option>
                <option>Delhi NCR</option>
                <option>Bangalore</option>
                <option>Hyderabad</option>
                <option>Chennai</option>
                <option>Pune</option>
                <option>Kolkata</option>
                <option>Ahmedabad</option>
                <option>Jaipur</option>
                <option>Kochi</option>
                <option>Lucknow</option>
                <option>Chandigarh</option>
                <option>Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="carBrand">Car Brand *</label>
              <select id="carBrand" name="carBrand" required>
                <option value="">Select Brand</option>
                <option>Maruti Suzuki</option>
                <option>Hyundai</option>
                <option>Tata</option>
                <option>Mahindra</option>
                <option>Honda</option>
                <option>Toyota</option>
                <option>Kia</option>
                <option>MG</option>
                <option>Volkswagen</option>
                <option>Skoda</option>
                <option>BMW</option>
                <option>Mercedes-Benz</option>
                <option>Audi</option>
                <option>Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="service">Service Needed *</label>
            <select id="service" name="service" required>
              <option value="">Select Service</option>
              <option>Basic Service (₹2,999+)</option>
              <option>Comprehensive Service (₹5,499+)</option>
              <option>AC Service & Repair (₹1,999+)</option>
              <option>Denting & Painting (₹2,499+)</option>
              <option>Tyres & Wheel Care (₹999+)</option>
              <option>Battery Replacement (₹3,499+)</option>
              <option>Car Detailing (₹999+)</option>
              <option>Insurance Claim</option>
              <option>Multiple Services</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Get Free Quote Now</button>
          <p class="form-note">No spam. No obligation. Your data is secure with us.</p>
        </form>
        <div class="form-success" id="formSuccess">
